{"tid":2461213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"長賜輪卡蘇伊士運河 長榮海運保留對日本船東求償權利","createTime":"2021-03-25T09:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T10:50:58.000Z","uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0190d3595086a18a027a40f4250b57dcd2be74b7","tid":2461213,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3478684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3478684&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=e8db2651\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3478684&h=b32d4f9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3478684</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者王憶紅／台北報導〕長榮海運長賜輪卡在蘇伊士運河一事，引發喧然大波，市場更傳出後續恐有百億美元賠償，但市場人士指出，長榮海運因向日本船東租船，因此可向船東保留求償權利。<br />\n<br />\n長賜輪是長榮海運以論時傭船（Time Charter）方式向日本船東承租，也就是船、船員由船東負責，長榮海運只出租金、油錢。<br />\n<br />\n對於市場擔心長榮海運恐遭賠一事，長榮海運表示，目前正全力協調相關單位排除事故，儘速協助這艘擱淺的租船脫困，以恢復正常航行，日後若有賠償訴求，將在事故調查報告出爐，釐清責任之後，與船東公司討論後續相關事宜。"},{"pid":"836df83df16995883a3537ded0f40afd9b7a225a","tid":2461213,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"長榮只係負責租船，賠償金應該會由日本負責，而唔係網上傳由台灣負責"},{"pid":"aa315044df2afc5a0ea010c36252c3044012b9e4","tid":2461213,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"836df83df16995883a3537ded0f40afd9b7a225a","tid":2461213,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"長榮只係負責租船，賠償金應該會由日本負責，而唔係網上傳由台灣負責"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"船身上面D英文字唔係寫住&quot;長榮&quot;？"},{"pid":"d81d60b890c4643ac819818fcadf5b9756098cbb","tid":2461213,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa315044df2afc5a0ea010c36252c3044012b9e4","tid":2461213,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"836df83df16995883a3537ded0f40afd